channel.title: [Unicorn Challenge :unicorn:] Insurgency LP Remix Contest - Winners Announced
channel.description:
Hey everyone!
A few months ago, I hosted a remix contest for my song Wind. I had a lot of fun hosting it, and a bunch of people entered. ![Screenshot%20(1)|690x375](upload://qIL9ACUv6PY9r72aOaAfIuzzqYm.png) It's been a while, and I thought it would be a good idea to host another remix contest, this time with a unicorn :unicorn: as a prize.
As some of you may know, my debut album, Insurgency, came out about a month ago. For this remix contest, you can pick any track from the album to remix. There are 7 tracks (not including the prelude, interlude, and outro)
_____
[Insurgency LP :soundcloud: ](https://soundcloud.com/hydrans/sets/insurgency-lp) [details="Tracklist"] Track 1 - [Rotation](https://soundcloud.com/hydrans/rotation?in=hydrans/sets/insurgency-lp) Track 2 - [Insurgency](https://soundcloud.com/hydrans/insurgency?in=hydrans/sets/insurgency-lp) Track 3 - [Vortex](https://soundcloud.com/hydrans/vortex?in=hydrans/sets/insurgency-lp) Track 4 - [Purple Magic](https://soundcloud.com/hydrans/purple-magic?in=hydrans/sets/insurgency-lp) Track 5 - [Hachiwara (w/ Aqzi)](https://soundcloud.com/hydrans/hachiwara?in=hydrans/sets/insurgency-lp) Track 6 - [Antithesis (w/ Mr Mooo)](https://soundcloud.com/hydrans/antithesis?in=hydrans/sets/insurgency-lp) Track 7 - [Creature](https://soundcloud.com/hydrans/creature?in=hydrans/sets/insurgency-lp) [/details]
____
<big>**How to enter**</big>
To enter the contest, please @mention me in this thread and I will PM you with the project file on the disco. Please specify which song you are remixing. You could also PM me directly, or DM me on Discord at HYDRANS#0999. ___
<big>**Rules**</big>
1. Tracks must be at least 1:30 in length to qualify
2. Tracks must be titled "HYDRANS - [Track Name] (___ Remix)" [spoiler]For the collabs, include the other artist's name as well.[/spoiler] 3. If possible, use this cover art: ![Copy%20of%20Copy%20of%20Untitled%20Design|500x500](upload://Liw9jPYLAdU3s0gA8ZbuBJ1YYh.jpeg) 4. Tracks must be uploaded to SoundCloud to be eligible for prizes (please post the link in this thread) 5. In order to win prizes, your remix should be submitted by March 31st, I will judge them the week of April 1st
There aren't any rules about how you should make the song. You have complete creative freedom!
______
<big>**Prizes!**</big>
[details="1st Place"] A unicorn :unicorn: on the disco, a repost on my SoundCloud, and a collab with me [/details]
[details="2nd Place"] A unicorn :unicorn: on the disco, and a repost on my SoundCloud, and a collab with me [/details]
[details="3rd Place"] A repost on my SoundCloud [/details]
[details="4th Place"] A repost on my SoundCloud [/details]
All eligible remixes will be featured in a playlist on SoundCloud.
_____
Good luck to everyone entering! If you have any questions, I am happy to answer them!
Thanks! ~ HYDRANS

item.title: [Unicorn Challenge :unicorn:] Insurgency LP Remix Contest - Winners Announced
item.dc:creator: HYDRANS
item.description:
Alright, I’m finally done judging!

Before I say who won, I really want to thank everyone who entered. All of the entries were so good, and it was really hard to decide the winners.

Winners

4th Place (click for more details) 3rd Place (click for more details) 2nd Place (click for more details) Honorable Mention (click for more details)

And finally…

1st Place! (click for more details)

Prizing

First of all, everyone who entered will be featured in a playlist featuring all of the remixes on my SoundCloud page.

The 3rd and 4th place winners will have their remix reposted on my SoundCloud until next Sunday. Also, you get glory and honor for making awesome remixes!

The 1st and 2nd place winners will get a repost on my SoundCloud also, as well as an opportunity for a collaboration with me. Oh yeah, and you win a unicorn that will be displayed next to your name on the Auxy Disco!

If you have any other questions about prizing, feel free to ask me.

Here is the playlist with all of the remixes: https://soundcloud.com/hydrans/sets/hydrans-insurgency-lp-remixes

Make sure to share this playlist so you can support everyone else who entered!

Thanks again!
~ HYDRANS
